 be added to the map view at this time.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Any multipoint, multipolyline, multipolygon, shape or point collection","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that is specified is silently ignored.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"Note"},{"level":4,"type":"heading","text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples"},{"style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Add a line annotation from GeoJSON.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"To Do"},{"style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Add an annotation to an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"To Do"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)addAnnotation:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"addAnnotation:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1793"},"symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/addannotation:"]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the map view."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/addAnnotation:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/addAnnotation:","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the map view."}],"title":"addAnnotation:","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/addannotation:","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMultiPolyline","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"disconnected vertices, specified as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"text":" instances. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"orchard.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNPointCollection","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointCollection","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"title":"MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPolyline"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","title":"MLNPolyline","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the line segments that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path along which something moves."}]}}}